import React, { Component } from "react";
import {
  MDBContainer,
  MDBBtn,
  MDBInputGroup,
  MDBInput,
  MDBModal,
  MDBModalBody,
  MDBModalHeader,
  MDBModalFooter,
  MDBCol, MDBRow, MDBCard, MDBCardUp, MDBCardBody, MDBAvatar, MDBRotatingCard, MDBIcon 
} from "mdbreact";


<MDBModalBody>
<MDBInput label="Nom Prénom" outline />
<MDBInput label="Age" outline />
<MDBInput label="Photo" outline />
<MDBInputGroup
  containerClassName="mb-3"
  prepend="Sexe"
  inputs={
    <select className="browser-default custom-select">
      <option value="0">Choisir...</option>
      <option value="1">Femme</option>
      <option value="2">Homme</option>
    </select>
  }
/>
<MDBInput label="Numéro téléphone" outline />
<MDBInput label="Ville" outline />
<MDBInput label="Disponibilité" outline />

<MDBInput label="Expérience" outline />
</MDBModalBody>
